<div class="page">

  <!-- SIDEBAR -->
  <aside class="sidebar">
    <nav class="sidebar-nav">
      <button class="sidebar-link active" data-tab="faq">FAQ</button>
      <button class="sidebar-link" data-tab="sizing">Sizing &amp; Care</button>
      <button class="sidebar-link" data-tab="shipping">Shipping &amp; Delivery</button>
      <button class="sidebar-link" data-tab="returns">Returns</button>
      <button class="sidebar-link" data-tab="contact">Contact</button>
    </nav>
  </aside>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <main class="content">

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="panel active" data-panel="faq">
      <h1 class="panel-title">Frequently asked</h1>
      <p class="panel-intro">Everything you might want to know before, during, and after your order. If your question isn't here, we're a short message away.</p>

      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">What size should I order?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Our pieces are designed with a relaxed, considered fit. For your closest match, refer to the size chart under Sizing &amp; Care.</p>
            <p>Each product page also lists the height and size worn by the model in our editorial imagery, which can be a helpful reference.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">How do I track my order?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>When your order is dispatched from our warehouse, you'll receive an email from Hello@cieristudio.com with your tracking number and a tracking link. You'll be able to track your order within 24-48 hours of receiving the email. Once you click your tracking number, you'll be taken to the shipping carrier's page, where you can see detailed tracking information for your order.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">When will my order ship?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>In-stock orders are dispatched within 1-3 business days. You'll receive a confirmation email with tracking once your order is on its way.</p>
            <p>Pre-order and made-to-order pieces ship on the date listed on the product page.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Do you ship internationally?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Yes, we ship worldwide. Shipping rates are calculated at checkout. For full delivery times and rates by region, see Shipping &amp; Delivery.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Do I have to purchase in USD?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>No. You can shop in the currency of your preference. Go to the top right of the screen and choose your currency, you can now shop in USD, CAD, AUD, GBP and EUR.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Can I return or exchange an item?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Returns are accepted within 14 days of delivery, provided pieces are unworn, unwashed, and have their original tags attached. Returns are refunded as store credit, which never expires. We don't offer direct exchanges, so simply return your piece for credit and place a new order. Return shipping is arranged and paid by you. Discounted items and gift cards are final sale.</p>
            <p>Full details, including how to initiate a return, are under Returns.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">What if my order arrives damaged or faulty?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>While we do our very best to ensure this never happens, if you receive a damaged piece or a manufacturing fault occurs, please contact us immediately at Hello@cieristudio.com and we'll do our best to resolve it. After 45 days from receiving the product, any damage is considered wear and tear rather than a manufacturing fault.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Received something you didn't order?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>If you received a product different from the one you ordered, please contact us at Hello@cieristudio.com and we'll be sure to get you the pieces you ordered.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">How do I care for my CIERI pieces?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Our pieces are made to be lived in, which means cared for gently. As a general rule: machine wash cold with like colours, and lay flat out of direct sunlight to dry. For the full care guide, see Sizing &amp; Care or refer to the label sewn into each garment.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Can I cancel or change my order?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Once an order is placed, we're unable to make changes or cancellations, as pieces are prepared for dispatch quickly. Please review your size, shipping address, and order details carefully before completing checkout. If something is wrong, reach us via Contact as soon as possible and we'll help where we can.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">What if the product I want is sold out?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Be sure to subscribe on the product page to be notified when the item has been restocked.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Have a question we haven't answered?<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Don't hesitate to reach out to us or email at Hello@cieristudio.com for any additional questions and concerns.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- SIZING -->
    <div class="panel" data-panel="sizing">
      <h1 class="panel-title">Sizing &amp; care</h1>
      <p class="panel-intro">All measurements are in centimetres, taken from the garment laid flat. If you're between sizes, size down for fitted silhouettes and up for relaxed ones.</p>

      <h2 class="size-section-title">Tops &amp; Tanks</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
      <table class="size-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Size</th><th>Bust</th><th>Waist</th><th>Length</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>S</td><td>66-86</td><td>56-76</td><td>45</td></tr>
          <tr><td>M</td><td>70-90</td><td>60-80</td><td>46</td></tr>
          <tr><td>L</td><td>74-94</td><td>64-84</td><td>47</td></tr>
          <tr><td>XL</td><td>80-100</td><td>70-90</td><td>48</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="size-section-title">Bottoms</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
      <table class="size-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Size</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hips</th><th>Thigh</th><th>Pants (Reg)</th><th>Pants (Petite)</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>S</td><td>54-74</td><td>82-102</td><td>46-56</td><td>104</td><td>94</td></tr>
          <tr><td>M</td><td>56-76</td><td>86-106</td><td>48-58</td><td>105</td><td>96</td></tr>
          <tr><td>L</td><td>58-78</td><td>90-110</td><td>50-60</td><td>106</td><td>98</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      </div>
      <p class="size-caption">Pants come in Regular and Petite lengths.</p>

      <h2 class="size-section-title">Skirts</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
      <table class="size-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Size</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hips</th><th>Length</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>S</td><td>58-78</td><td>72-92</td><td>99</td></tr>
          <tr><td>M</td><td>62-82</td><td>74-94</td><td>100</td></tr>
          <tr><td>L</td><td>66-86</td><td>78-98</td><td>101</td></tr>
          <tr><td>XL</td><td>70-90</td><td>84-104</td><td>102</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="size-section-title">Dresses</h2>
      <div class="size-table-wrap">
      <table class="size-table">
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Size</th><th>Bust</th><th>Waist</th><th>Hip</th><th>Length</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>XS</td><td>84</td><td>66</td><td>90</td><td>108</td></tr>
          <tr><td>S</td><td>88</td><td>70</td><td>94</td><td>109</td></tr>
          <tr><td>M</td><td>92</td><td>74</td><td>98</td><td>110</td></tr>
          <tr><td>L</td><td>96</td><td>78</td><td>102</td><td>111</td></tr>
          <tr><td>XL</td><td>100</td><td>82</td><td>106</td><td>112</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      </div>

      <h2 class="size-section-title">Care</h2>
      <ul class="care-list">
        <li>Machine wash in cold water with like colours.</li>
        <li>Lay garments separately flat out of direct sunlight to dry.</li>
        <li>Ensure garments are completely dry prior to storing.</li>
        <li>Avoid contact with rough surfaces as it can cause fabric pulling.</li>
        <li>To avoid staining or marking your garments, take care with perfumes, deodorants, body lotions and makeup, and allow them to dry fully before dressing.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- SHIPPING -->
    <div class="panel" data-panel="shipping">
      <h1 class="panel-title">Shipping &amp; delivery</h1>
      <p class="panel-intro">We ship worldwide. Once your order is on its way, you'll receive a confirmation email with tracking.</p>

      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Processing time<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Orders are processed within 1-3 business days. During sale periods and holidays, processing may take a little longer.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Shipping rates &amp; delivery<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Shipping rates are calculated at checkout based on your destination. Estimated delivery times after dispatch:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Southeast Asia (Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, the Philippines):</strong> 5-7 business days</li>
              <li><strong>Europe, the UK, North America, and Australia:</strong> 10-15 business days</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Delivery estimates are not guaranteed, as transit can be affected by customs and the carrier.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Duties &amp; taxes<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>International orders may be subject to import duties and taxes set by your country. These are not included at checkout and are the responsibility of the customer, usually collected by the carrier on delivery.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Lost, stolen, or delayed packages<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Once your order is handed to the carrier, CIERI cannot take responsibility for parcels that are lost, stolen, delayed, or delivered to an incorrect address entered at checkout. If your parcel is missing, check with your neighbours, building reception, and any safe spots near your door, then contact us and we will do our best to help.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RETURNS -->
    <div class="panel" data-panel="returns">
      <h1 class="panel-title">Returns</h1>
      <p class="panel-intro">We want every CIERI piece to feel right. If it doesn't, eligible items can be returned within 14 days of delivery for store credit.</p>

      <div class="accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Our returns policy<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>You have 14 days from the date your order is delivered to request a return. To be eligible, items must be returned in their original condition:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>New, unworn, unwashed, and undamaged</li>
              <li>Free of odours, stains, makeup, deodorant, and pet hair</li>
              <li>With all original tags, hygiene stickers, and packaging attached and intact</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We inspect every return and reserve the right to decline any item that does not meet these requirements. Sale and discounted items, and gift cards, are final sale and cannot be returned.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Store credit<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>All approved returns are refunded as store credit, issued for the full value of the returned item. Store credit does not expire and can be used on any future order. We do not offer refunds to the original payment method.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">How to start a return<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Email us at Hello@cieristudio.com with your order number and the item or items you would like to return. We will confirm your return and share the return address. Please wait for our confirmation before sending anything back, as items returned without prior authorisation cannot be accepted.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Return shipping<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Return shipping is arranged and paid by the customer. We recommend a tracked service, as we cannot take responsibility for returns lost in transit. Original shipping charges are non-refundable. For international returns, any customs duties or taxes incurred in sending an item back are the customer's responsibility.</p>
            <p>Items from different orders must be returned separately, each under its own return confirmation.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Exchanges<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>We do not offer direct exchanges. To change a size or colour, return your item for store credit and place a new order for the piece you would like.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Changes &amp; cancellations<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Once an order is placed we begin processing it right away and cannot make changes or cancellations. Please review your size, items, and address carefully before checking out.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <button class="accordion-trigger">Fair use of returns<svg class="accordion-chevron" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg></button>
          <div class="accordion-content"><div class="accordion-body">
            <p>Our return policy is offered in good faith. We reserve the right to limit or decline returns, or to restrict future orders, for accounts that show a pattern of excessive returns of non-faulty items.</p>
          </div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CONTACT -->
    <div class="panel" data-panel="contact">
      <h1 class="panel-title">Contact</h1>
      <p class="panel-intro">For anything we haven't answered here, write to us. We respond within one business day, often sooner.</p>

      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div>
          <h3 class="contact-block-title">Customer care</h3>
          <p class="contact-block-detail">Hello@cieristudio.com<br>Monday to Friday, 09:00–17:00 AEST</p>
        </div>

        <form class="contact-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Thank you. We will be in touch shortly.');">
          <div>
            <label for="cf-name">Name</label>
            <input type="text" id="cf-name" required>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="cf-email">Email</label>
            <input type="email" id="cf-email" required>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="cf-subject">Subject</label>
            <input type="text" id="cf-subject" required>
          </div>
          <div>
            <label for="cf-message">Message</label>
            <textarea id="cf-message" required></textarea>
          </div>
          <button type="submit" class="contact-submit">Send message</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Customer care page",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Customer care page"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
